A ranar Asabar, a kalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu bayan wata girgizar kasa da tsunami ta ritsa da tsibirin Indonesiya na Sulawesi, kamar yadda hukumomi suka ruwaito, tare da manyan raƙuman ruwa da ke kwashe yawancin su.
Daruruwan mutane sun taru don yin biki a bakin rairayin bakin teku na garin Palou a ranar Juma'a, yayin da raƙuman ruwa masu tsayin mita shida (18 feet) suka yi ta kai hari ga bakin teku cikin duhu, suna hallaka duk abin da ke cikin hanyarsu.
Tsunami ya fara ne bayan girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5.
"A lokacin da barazanar tsunami ta faru a jiya, mutane suna kan rairayin bakin teku suna ci gaba da ayyukansu, kuma sun mutu ba tare da sun gudu daga wurin ba, "in ji Suwo Puro Nugroho, wakilin kamfanin dillancin labaran Indonesiya, wanda ke taimakawa da sakamakon bala'i a Jakarta.
Tsunami ba shi kaɗai ya zo ba, ya bi shi da motoci, itatuwa, gidaje, da sauransu, in ji Nugroho, ya kuma kara da cewa tsunami ya fara zuwa cikin teku a cikin teku mai zurfi na 800 km / h (497 mi / h) kafin ya buga bakin teku.
Wasu mutane sun tsere daga tsunami ta hanyar hawa bishiyoyi, kuma wannan shine kawai dalilin da yasa suka tsira, in ji shi.
An kwashe mutane kusan 16700 zuwa cibiyoyi 24 a cikin garin Palou.
