Amurka za ta ninka kudin da ta kashe kan kera fasahar AI
Yayin da China ke da karfi a fannin ilimin kere kere, Amurka za ta ninka kudin da take kashewa wajen gudanar da bincike kan wannan fannin, a cewar mai zuba jari kuma mai binciken ilimin kere kere a kamfanonin Google, Microsoft da Apple, Kai-Fu Li.
Irin wannan tsokaci ya faru ne bayan da wasu sassan gwamnatin Amurka suka ba da rahoton AI, duk da cewa Amurka ba ta da wata dabarar ci gaban AI ta yau da kullun.
A halin yanzu, China ta gabatar da shirin shekara ta biyu: tana son zama ta farko a cikin abubuwan kirkire-kirkire ta 2030.
"Da yake sauran kasashe suna da yawa a baya fiye da Amurka, zai zama da kyau a ninka kasafin kudin binciken AI, muna neman ci gaba a fannin AI", in ji Li.
