Mista Evo Morales, shugaban kasar Bolivia mai tasiri wanda ya fito daga 'yan asalin kasar - wanda ke fuskantar sake zaben da ake ta yin rigima a shekara mai zuwa - ya kasance cikin tsaka mai wuya sakamakon hukuncin da kotun ta yanke a ranar Litinin.
A watan Agustan da ya gabata, ya yi alwashi cewa "za mu dawo da tekun Pacific a cikinmu ba da daɗewa ba".
Amma duk da haka, wasu masu sharhi sun yi imanin cewa hukuncin kotun ba zai yi nasara ba a kan Bolivia, amma ba abin da zai canza.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya da ke Netherlands ba ta da ikon yin tasiri a kan yankin Jamhuriyar Chile, saboda haka ba za a iya tantance abin da za a yi a tattaunawar ta gaba ba.
Wani masanin shari'a na kasa da kasa na Jamhuriyar Chile, Pas Sarate, ya yi sharhi game da wannan yanayin a cikin kalmomi masu zuwa: "Hukuncin kotun kasa da kasa bayan watanni shida bayan sauraron karshe ya nuna cewa wannan mataki ba shi da wuya".
