Washington na iya amfani da sojojin ruwa don fitar da makamashi na Rasha idan ya cancanta, kamar yadda ya shafi Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Ministan cikin gida na Amurka Ryan Zinke, wanda ya ruwaito The Washington Examiner.
A cewar Zinke, Rasha ba ta shiga cikin Syria ba don komai, musamman ma abubuwan da Gwamnatin Shari'a ta kira kawai don bincika kasuwar makamashi.
"Ina tsammanin dalilin da ya sa Rasha ta zama baƙo a Gabas ta Tsakiya shine cewa suna yin sulhu a cikin fannin makamashi, saboda wannan shine yanayin gabas da kudancin Turai", in ji ministan.
A cewar shugabannin, akwai hanyoyi da dama da za a iya magance wannan matsala.
"Amurka tana da damar cewa Sojojin Ruwa na Amurka suna buɗewa kuma ba za su iya samun damar samun albarkatun makamashi a kasuwa ba idan ya cancanta", in ji shi.
Zincke ya yi kira ga mahalarta taron kungiyar masu amfani da makamashi na Alliance of Energy Users, wanda ya bayyana kansu a matsayin "muryar masu amfani da makamashi na Amurka".
Ya kwatanta matsayin Washington da na Rasha da Iran, yana mai cewa sun yi kama da juna.
