A ranar Laraba da ta gabata, shugaban Amurka D. Trump ya zargi China da yin magudi a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka da za a yi a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, inda ya yi tsokaci kan wani jaridar Iowa da aka buga a jaridar Des Moines Register, inda ya yi tallan tallace-tallace da aka biya a shafinsa na China Daily, amma China ta musanta zargin.
