Saboda katsewar sadarwa, ma'aikatan agaji ba su iya samun bayanai daga gundumar Donggala da ke arewacin Palu, kusa da cibiyar girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5.
Fiye da mutane 16000 a Palu an kwashe bayan bala'in.
