Palua babban birni ne na lardin Central Sulawesi, wanda ke kan bakin gabar tsibirin Sulawesi, wanda ke da mazaunan 379800 a shekara ta 2017.
A lokacin da garin ke bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwa, girgizar ƙasa da tsunami sun faru.
Donggala shi ne gundumar da ke da nisan fiye da kilomita 300 (180 mi) a gabar arewa maso yammacin Sulawesi.
A cikin yankin da ke ƙarƙashin lardin, gundumar, a cikin shekara ta 2017, yawan mutane 299200 ne.
