A cikin 'yan shekarun nan, an yi girgizar ƙasa da tsunami masu tsanani kamar su:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta haifar da tsunami a gabar tekun yamma na lardin Aceh na Indonesia, arewacin Sumatra. Mutane 226000 sun mutu a cikin ƙasashe 14 da ke Tekun Indiya - fiye da rabin su mazauna Aceh.
A ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu, an yi girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a bakin tekun yammacin Sumatra, wanda ya sa aka yi girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi sau biyu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias a gabar Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 6.8 a kudancin tsibirin Java, mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami a kudancin bakin teku, inda mutane 700 suka mutu.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta auku kusa da Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Fiye da mutane 1100 suka mutu.
2010: A daya daga cikin tsibirin Mentawai kusa da Sumatra, an yi girgizar kasa mai girman 7.5, wanda ya haifar da tsunami mai tsawon sama da mita 10, ya lalata ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kwashe kusan mutane 300.
2016: A cikin Piidijaja County a Aceh, ƙaramin girgizar ƙasa ta haifar da rushewa da tsoro, yayin da mutane ke tuna mummunan sakamakon girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a 2004.
