A 2018, ƙungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup da aka yi a Le Golf National a Paris, Faransa, inda ta ci Amurka da ƙidayar 16,5-10,5.
Amurka ta yi rashin nasara a Turai sau shida a jere kuma ba ta lashe Kofin Ryder a Turai ba tun 1993.
Kyaftin din Denmark Thomas Bjorn ya lashe kambin Turai bayan da tawagarsa ta samu maki 14,5 da ake bukata don cin nasarar Amurka.
Tauraron Amurka, Phil Mikelson, wanda ya yi gwagwarmaya a mafi yawan lokacin gasar, ya jefa kwallon a 3-point na rami na 16, kuma ya ci nasara da Franchesco Molinari.
A Italiyanci golfer Molivarini ya haskaka a duk yawon shakatawa, da na yanzu format na gasar ya kasance mai kunnawa 1-4 wanda ya tafi 5-0-0 tun 1979.
Jordan Smith daga Amurka ta sha kashi da ci 5-4 a hannun Danish Torbjern Olesen, mafi ƙarancin darajar ƙungiyar Turai.
Mafi kyawun ɗan wasan duniya, Dustin Johnson, ya buga wasan ƙarshe a gasar Ryder Cup, inda ya ci Ingila da Ian Pultre da 2 da 1.
Tsohon sojan Ryder Cup takwas, Spaniyar Sergio Garcia ya zama mafi kyawun nasara a gasar Turai tare da ƙididdigar 25,5.
"Ba na yawan kuka, amma yau ba zan iya yin kuka ba.
Wannan shekara ta kasance mai wahala.
Don haka ina son in gode wa Thomas da ya zaɓe ni kuma ya amince da ni.
Ina farin ciki sosai, ina farin ciki da dawowar kofin.
Wannan shi ne game da tawagar, kuma ina farin ciki da na iya taimaka", ya ce Garcia emotionally bayan lashe a Turai.
Ya ba da fitila ga ɗan'uwansa John Ram, wanda ya ci wasan golf na Amurka Tiger Woods a ranar Lahadi da 2 da 1.
"Ina alfahari da nasarar da na yi a Tiger Woods, saboda na yi girma ina kallon wannan saurayin", in ji Ram, mai shekara 23.
Wods ya lashe dukkan wasanni hudu a Faransa kuma yanzu ya kafa rikodin 13-21-3 na Ryder Cup.
Ya lashe manyan lakabi 14, ba kawai ya iya doke Jack Nicklaus ba, abin da ya zama lissafi mai ban mamaki ga ɗaya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasa a kowane lokaci.
Teamungiyar Amurka ta yi ƙoƙari ta sami ferweys a ƙarshen mako, ta bar Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Final, waɗanda suka buga wasan golf a babban matakin.
Kyaftin Amurka Jim Furik ya ce bayan wasan rashin nasara na tawagarsa: "Ina alfahari da waɗannan samarin, sun yi yaƙi.
A yau, Turai ta ɗan yi zafi da safe.
Mun ba da kanmu.
Ina jin murna a gaban Tom.
Shi babban kyaftin ne.
Dukkanin 'yan wasansa 12 sun yi wasa sosai.
Za mu hada kai, za mu yi aiki tare da kwamitin Ryder Cup na Amurka, za mu ci gaba.
Ina ƙaunar waɗannan 'yan'uwa 12 kuma ina alfahari da na yi hidima a matsayin kyaftin.
Ya kamata ku cire kayanku.
An yi nasara da mu. "
